name: Sonsaku Hakufu (Ikkitousen)
description:
Lora model of Sonsaku Hakufu from Ikkitousen. Preview images were made with weight 1. I would advise lowering it to 0.8-0.9 for full body images because it was trained mostly on cowboy shots and legs can get messy.

I spent few days trying to make new version of one of my older models and failed miserably TwT so I turned to big booba again. Big booba, good feels, waku waku ^_^

Also it was requested.

Only one outfit really and prompt is: sonsaku hakufu, earrings, red bow, sweater vest, white shirt, plaid skirt, white socks, loafers

You can add fingerless gloves too cause that's part of outfit most of time, but I tend to skip it cause it just complicates hands.
